Class QuoteSubMsgSelector

java.lang.Object
  quoteSubMsgSelector.QuoteSubMsgSelector

public class QuoteSubMsgSelector
extends java.lang.Object

Basically, QuoteSubMsgSelector is exactly the same as QuoteSubscriberB The essential change is that in this class, watchList doesn't hold QuoteSubscriber, but MsgSelector, which is inherited from QuoteSubscriber
